{"tid":2211212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"朱凱廸稱雷達可監察12港人船隻路線　促當局發放資訊","createTime":"2020-09-21T03:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T17:36:18.000Z","uid":241764,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9d07826ce02127e3cf7d726b7c980bcc90b59517","tid":2211212,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"12名港人早前涉嫌非法入境內地水域，至今仍在深圳刑事拘留。立法會議員朱凱廸說，目前只知道12人在內地水域被捕，但他們是由香港潛逃，而本港當局有雷達可監察船隻航行路線，認為當局應發放有關他們在香港水域的行動資訊。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550741-20200921.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550741-20200921.htm&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZotOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=18b36223\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550741-20200921.htm&h=4997b548\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550741-20200921.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6553c2f78a92c81f458eac0f9f153b080758ca84","tid":2211212,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:40:46.000Z","msg":"唉唔知講咩好<br />\n唔確定呢班泛民真係幫緊手"},{"pid":"d8328aec7c070573cbde2f7edc7603a999e1e3b0","tid":2211212,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"發放咗啲人都唔會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd787296e9d6e62d0f90b0e93e0c0b94b676a7ce","tid":2211212,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"問題係radar未必睇到<br />\n同埋你一開始要track到佢隻船先，即係你要知到佢係邊到，幾點開船先track到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae66986954edd9edb73e94215f96bb912677d7b2","tid":2211212,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:44:28.000Z","msg":"咁佢咪做個假雷達圖出嚟塞住你把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時你話佢造假？證實